<p><img height="391" src="Images/music/edited/areas-of-study/organ/OrganStakeCenter2.jpg" width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>a three-manual, 9-rank Rodgers organ in Taylor Chapel</strong></p>
<ol><ol>
